  "title": "Sales Executive (B2B) #81724",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Workwear / Safety Apparel Industry</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Executive (B2B)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tai Seng</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday – Friday, 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS + Bonus + Allowances + Medical Benefits</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Service existing customers and support business development by bringing in new accounts.</li><li>Communicate with suppliers and customers to follow up on orders and enquiries.</li><li>Prepare sales documents such as quotations, tenders, purchase orders, and delivery orders.</li><li>Plan and coordinate delivery schedules.</li><li>Work towards agreed sales targets.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Good interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Able to work independently with minimal supervision.</li><li>Experience in the garment/workwear industry, corporate gifts, or kitchenware (restaurant) supplies is an advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81724 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
